net.sf.jboard.model.forum.dto
Interface IForumComponent

All Known Implementing Classes:
ForumCategory, ForumItem, ForumMessage, ForumThread
public interface IForumComponent

Interface for ForumCategory and Messages classes. this Interface is the Component interface in the design Pattern Composite (GoF). ForumCategory is Composite, and ForumMessage is Leaf.

Version:
$Revision: 1.10 $
Author:
